<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,730,1804,1830]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
Key to the Indo-Pacific species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sensu Randall" authorityYear="2005" box="[572,725,1804,1830]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Kyphosidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Kyphosidae</taxonomicName>
:
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
